name: DAI
description: Luxury lighter manufacturer S.T. Dupont continues to innovate with the Defi Extreme series, a lighter whose performance is off the charts. The dynamic and distinguished design makes the Defi Extreme lighters a true symbol of performance, its innovative construction combining a precision-engineered metal lighter body with a matte black plastic jacket to protect the metal body. Intuitive functionality and tactile features make the S.T. Dupont Defi Extrem lighters an everyday lighter for any purpose
